  <div class="panel panel-info" style:"margin-top:-10px;">
    <h4 id="index-header"><label id="maeven-landing">The Maeven Collective</label> a comprehensive online catalogue of the best resources, tools and networks for the female creative entrepreneur.</h4>
  </div>

